INCLUDES EVERYTHING YOU NEED for a smooth laundry experience, like a measuring detergent cup for precise usage, a folding silicone funnel for spill-free refills, a laundry detergent cap for secure storage, and a sleek white tray that organizes all your essentials

GAIN VALUABLE LAUNDRY INSIGHTS with an included e-book full of tips and tricks. With this laundry liquid dispenser set, you can now make the most of your washing set-up. For all-inclusive laundry room organization and storage, click 'ADD TO CART'!

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Streamline Your Laundry Process Introducing Cleaniverse's Laundry Detergent Containers — a practical solution that simplifies your laundry chores while adding elegance to your laundry area!
Streamline Your Laundry Process Introducing Cleaniverse's Laundry Detergent Containers — a practical solution that simplifies your laundry chores while adding elegance to your laundry area!

Unleash the Ultimate Laundry Kit! In this set, you'll find two liquid containers, each holding a generous 64 oz of detergent and white silicone covers that provide a secure, non-slip grip. Moreover, there's a white tray included for perfect organization, two measuring cups for accurate dispensing, a silicone folding funnel for easy refills, and two storage caps to keep your detergent tightly sealed. What sets these containers apart is their high-volume pump, allowing you to effortlessly dispense 15ml with each pump. And to elevate your laundry experience further, we've thoughtfully included an eBook brimming with valuable tips and tricks.

Clear Labels, Clear Choice No more guessing which bottle is which — our set comes with four label stickers that allow you to instantly identify softener or detergent, and the other two are customizable so you can tailor fit them according to your needs. What's even better? They're fully waterproof! No matter how damp your hands get, these labels remain clear and legible. We know laundry days can get hectic too, which is why we've chosen to craft our containers from robust PET plastic, ensuring they don't leak, break, or crack easily. Say goodbye to the chaos of laundry day with the Cleaniverse Laundry Detergent Container Set!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Space Saver, Functionality and Look
reviews.reviewText: I recently considered adding a laundry detergent dispenser to my tight laundry area, and I couldn't be happier with its performance and innovative design. Because I don't have a separate laundry room, my units are in my kitchen. This space-saving addition has proven to be a game-changer in terms of functionality. The pump dispenser worked well. In a world where every inch of space counts, this sleek design will de-clutter my laundry area significantly. The design makes any laundry routine more streamlined. The dispenser housing has a high-quality silicon cover, and it's a standout feature for multiple reasons. It ensures durability and longevity, standing up to the daily wear and tear of a busy laundry room. The dispenser's silicon housing is not only functional but also aesthetically pleasing, adding a modern touch to my laundry space. All the extra items included in the bundle add value. Packaging and content overall are good. Highly recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Love everything but the drip
reviews.reviewText: I love the design, the concept and the size of these dispensers. They are so functional and convenient. I wanted it to pour my large Costco size Downy into something because the big container wasn’t functional for me. This pump makes it great to pump and go but I did notice it drips. Luckily it comes with a tray and cup, so I can sit the cup in front of it to catch the drips. The drip is the only thing I didn’t like but it’s not a deal breaker.
